Seo Mal-tae.

53
00:04:55,962 --> 00:04:57,964
Meneer Seo, ik heb over u gehoord.

54
00:04:58,047 --> 00:04:59,674
Was u ooit rechercheur?

55
00:04:59,757 --> 00:05:01,467
Ik heb jarenlange ervaring.

56
00:05:01,551 --> 00:05:04,554
Ik zal heel secuur werken.

57
